1. *Mirna* reka teče pored mog sela. (*Peaceful* river flows next to my village.)
2. Uveče je *mirno* u mom kraju. (It is *quiet* in my neighborhood in the evening.)
3. Ona je *mirno* sedela i gledala u daljinu. (She was sitting *calmly* and looking into the distance.)
4. *Mirnu* noć smo proveli u šatoru. (We spent a *peaceful* night in the tent.)
5. Ne možemo imati *mir* dokle god ima ratnih sukoba. (We cannot have *peace* as long as there are war conflicts.)
6. *Mirnoća* je važna za mentalno zdravlje. (*Serenity* is important for mental health.)
7. Predstava je bila jako *mirna*, ali emotivna. (The performance was very *subdued*, but emotional.)
8. Izvinjenje je dalo *mirnu* završnicu našoj raspravi. (The apology gave a *peaceful* ending to our argument.)
9. *Mirnu* površinu jezerca narušavaju samo patke. (Only ducks disturb the *calm* surface of the small lake.)
10. U kući vlada *mir*, jer deca spavaju. (*Peace* prevails in the house because the children are sleeping.)